rows.label: qst640102_msg0001
rows.name: Hey-ho.

rows.label: qst640102_msg0002
rows.name: Friends have business with Sisoso?
説明

rows.label: qst640102_msg0003
rows.name:
Oh, that story?
Is old, ah, "chestnut", yes.

rows.label: qst640102_msg0004
rows.name:
Which is to say, Sisoso talk about
needing special cylinder to salvage
boosters from Cloud Sea, yes.

rows.label: qst640102_msg0005
rows.name:
Never thought would see day when
someone here in Invidia want to salvage 
that, though. Big surprise, yes.

rows.label: qst640102_msg0006
rows.name:
Really, is cousinpon of Sisoso who
live in Avaritia who know all about
this stuff, but Sisoso try to help.

rows.label: qst640102_msg0007
rows.name:
If friends bring materials, me take
good old college try at making.

rows.label: qst640102_msg0008
rows.name:
First of all, need one Silver Cylinder
for use as base.

rows.label: qst640102_msg0009
rows.name:
Then, Zigzag Shaft. Can salvage up in
Avaritia if somewhat lucky!

rows.label: qst640102_msg0010
rows.name:
Lastly but not leastly, salvageable
item from Gula, Locust Spring.
...No no, better make it two!

rows.label: qst640102_msg0011
rows.name:
With those materials, Sisoso make
Booster Cylinder, just like cousinpon
taught!
シリンダ作成時＆以後ずっと配置

rows.label: qst640102_msg0101
rows.name:
Friends bring Sisoso materials for
make Booster Cylinder?
交換ショップ
作成したあと

rows.label: qst640102_msg0102
rows.name: There! Booster Cylinder is complete!

rows.label: qst640102_msg0103
rows.name:
Should try using at Salvage Point
on Lascham Island in Gula.

rows.label: qst640102_msg0104
rows.name:
Should come up with armloads of
boosters, meh!
感謝

rows.label: qst640102_msg0105
rows.name: Is nothing to mention, really.

rows.label: qst640102_msg0106
rows.name:
If friends ever need more, can come by
anytime.

rows.label: qst640102_msg0107
rows.name:
With every cylinder Sisoso make,
Sisoso get one step closer to equal
cousinpon in art of cylindercraft!
